<article id="post-752931" class="post-752931 digital-library type-digital-library status-publish has-post-thumbnail hentry category-architecture-and-hardware category-security-and-privacy issue-april-2024 section-practice">

			
<header class="article-header article-header--default">
	<div class="article-header__inner container">
		<div class="article-header__section"><a href="https://cacm.acm.org/section/practice/">Practice</a></div>
		<div class="article-header__topic-and-issue-section">
			<span class="article-header__topic">
			<a href="https://cacm.acm.org/category/architecture-and-hardware/">Architecture and Hardware</a>			</span>
			<span class="article-header__issue-section">
							</span>
		</div>
		<h1 class="article-header__title">Device Onboarding Using FDO and the Untrusted Installer Model</h1>
					<div class="article-header__subtitle"><p>FDO's untrusted model is contrasted with Wi-Fi Easy Connect to illustrate the advantages of each mechanism.</p>
</div>
		
		<div class="article-header__meta">
			<div class="article-header__byline">
				By <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/geoffrey-h-cooper/" title="Posts by Geoffrey H. Cooper" class="author url fn" rel="author">Geoffrey H. Cooper</a>			</div>
			<div class="article-header__posted-on">
				<span class="posted-on">Posted <time datetime="2024-03-11T16:14:02-04:00">Mar 11 2024</time></span>			</div>
		</div>

					<figure class="article-header__figure">
									<div class="image-wrapper image-wrapper--widescreen"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/030724.PR_.Device-Onboarding.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="network representation, illustration" loading="eager" decoding="async" srcset="https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/030724.PR_.Device-Onboarding.jpg 2400w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/030724.PR_.Device-Onboarding.jpg?resize=300,169 300w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/030724.PR_.Device-Onboarding.jpg?resize=768,432 768w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/030724.PR_.Device-Onboarding.jpg?resize=1024,576 1024w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/030724.PR_.Device-Onboarding.jpg?resize=1536,864 1536w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/030724.PR_.Device-Onboarding.jpg?resize=2048,1152 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></div>												</figure>
		
